{"tid":1285471,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"搭巴士返學 #11598搞既ebb網同六道仙人一樣用翻版借連登搵錢,點解只係刪曬post唔ban?,","createTime":"2019-07-04T14:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T06:56:00.000Z","uid":3020,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cb706eecbbad8a5f65f4ec54a7e1c0c3e0f1bcf8","tid":1285471,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:55:00.000Z","msg":"【動畫網】全新線上動畫網 <a href=\"http://ebb.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Febb.io&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRe2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=1d836ecf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ebb.io</a> 上線了！<br />\n<a href=\"https://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:iv17DFsBf1IJ:https://lihkg.com/thread/74559/page/1+&amp;cd=1&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;ct=clnk&amp;gl=hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebcache.googleusercontent.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dcache%3Aiv17DFsBf1IJ%3Ahttps%3A%2F%2Flihkg.com%2Fthread%2F74559%2Fpage%2F1%2B%26cd%3D1%26hl%3Dzh-TW%26ct%3Dclnk%26gl%3Dhk&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRe2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=fac84cbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:iv17DFsBf1IJ:https://lihkg.com/thread/74559/page/1+&amp;cd=1&amp;hl=zh-TW&amp;ct=clnk&amp;gl=hk</a><br />\n<br />\n由於各種營運開支不停上升<br />\n單靠廣告收入我們已連續數月赤字<br />\n<br />\n從 2019年7月1日 開始<br />\nebb 將改以贊助模式營運<br />\n各位可於 Patreon 上贊助我們<br />\n目前設有 2 種贊助計劃<br />\n也會提供限量的優惠版，名額先到先得<br />\n未贊助用戶將只能於非高峰時段觀看<br />\n贊助後即可獲取更好的觀看體驗<br />\n<br />\n我們明白這個決定對各位造成很大的不便<br />\n但為了維持健康的營運發展實在別無他法<br />\n我們也會移除網站上絕大部份的廣告<br />\n加快載入速度及提升瀏覧體驗<br />\n希望各位諒解並繼續支持我們 m(_ _)m<br />\n<br />\nebb終於開始收人錢.....<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1272792\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1272792</a>"},{"pid":"ddfb83263fc3d28a1233a1e9393a0d630c5bd603","tid":1285471,"uid":134665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:57:21.000Z","msg":"咪屈人哋"},{"pid":"8a919b904db4bc8f3f8f49a94cfde95f9a92006a","tid":12